'''原子朋克'''（'''{{lang-en|Atompunk}}'''）是一种受[[核子時代|核子時代]]影响的复古未来主义流派，主要流行於美國，結合[[冷戰時期|冷戰時期]]的核技術和80年代的復古風格，以原子科技發達的未來作為創作舞台，在早期的美式卡通或漫畫中可以見到。<ref name="Here Comes Atompunk">{{cite news | first=Bruce | last=Sterling | title=Here Comes 'Atompunk.' And It's Dutch. So there | url=https://www.wired.com/beyond_the_beyond/2008/12/here-comes-atom/ | date=2008-12-03 | access-date=2010-07-04 | work=Wired | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203172625/http://www.wired.com/beyond_the_beyond/2008/12/here-comes-atom/ | archive-date=2013-12-03 | url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Cory | last = Doctorow | title = Atompunk: fetishizing the atomic age | url = http://www.boingboing.net/2008/12/03/atompunk-fetishizing.html | publisher = [[Boing_Boing|Boing Boing]] | date = December 3, 2008 | access-date = 2015-06-25 | archive-date = 2022-01-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220110233257/https://boingboing.net/2008/12/03/atompunk-fetishizing.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

